When your med spa hits three locations, the cracks in entry-level software start showing. Consent forms live in five different folders. Treatment records don't sync between clinics. Your front desk spends 40 minutes daily on manual charting reconciliation. We've watched this pattern destroy operator sanity across hundreds of med spa portfolios.

Pabau and Zenoti both promise to solve these headaches, but they approach the problem from fundamentally different angles. After evaluating both platforms across dozens of med spa implementations—from single-location boutique clinics to 50+ location regional chains—our team has strong opinions on which tool fits which operator profile.

