<h2 id="final-verdict">🏆 Final Verdict</h2>

After implementing both platforms across dozens of med spa operations, our team recommends Pabau for the majority of aesthetic practice operators. The clinical documentation depth justifies the platform choice alone—when state boards audit your treatment records, Pabau's structured charting protects your license.

Zenoti earns consideration for enterprise operators where payroll complexity, retail scale, or franchise management requirements outweigh EMR priorities. If you're running a 30-location chain with 400 employees and significant skincare retail, Zenoti's operational toolset delivers value Pabau can't match.

The decision framework is straightforward: lead with clinical needs for practices under 20 locations, lead with operational complexity for larger portfolios. Most med spa operators fall into the first category.

